    {
      "id": "insight", "type": "text",
      "x": 30, "y": 440,
      "width": 720, "height": 40,
      "text": "Key insight: correction only matters when max CHANGES. In iter 2, max jumped from 3→4, so old O_acc must be scaled down.\nIn iter 3, max stayed at 4, so correction=1.0 — zero overhead. Early iters find true max; later iters are cheap.",
      "originalText": "Key insight: correction only matters when max CHANGES. In iter 2, max jumped from 3→4, so old O_acc must be scaled down.\nIn iter 3, max stayed at 4, so correction=1.0 — zero overhead. Early iters find true max; later iters are cheap.",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#64748b", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100
